-purple-300 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180","children":"▼"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/70 md:text-base","children":"Students from any recognized college/university can participate. Individual and team participation depends on the specific event rules."}]]}],["$","details","3️⃣ Is it necessary to bring a working project for the Ideathon?",{"className":"group rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/25 bg-black/35 px-5 py-4 text-white/85","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white marker:content-none md:text-base","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"3️⃣ Is it necessary to bring a working project for the Ideathon?"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-purple-300 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180","children":"▼"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/70 md:text-base","children":"No. The Ideathon focuses on idea pitching. Participants must present their concept using a PPT — no prototype or coding is required and PPT should be made in the venue after the topic is given."}]]}],["$","details","4️⃣ Can I participate in more than one event?",{"className":"group rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/25 bg-black/35 px-5 py-4 text-white/85","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white marker:content-none md:text-base","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"4️⃣ Can I participate in more than one event?"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-purple-300 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180","children":"▼"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/70 md:text-base","children":"Yes! Participants are allowed to register for multiple events, provided there are no schedule clashes."}]]}],["$","details","5️⃣ What is the refund policy?",{"className":"group rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/25 bg-black/35 px-5 py-4 text-white/85","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white marker:content-none md:text-base","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"5️⃣ What is the refund policy?"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-purple-300 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180","children":"▼"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/70 md:text-base","children":"Registrations are non-refundable 7 days before the event. Before that, 80% refund is issued within 5–7 business days."}]]}],["$","details","6️⃣ What is the dress code?",{"className":"group rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/25 bg-black/35 px-5 py-4 text-white/85","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white marker:content-none md:text-base","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"6️⃣ What is the dress code?"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-purple-300 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180","children":"▼"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/70 md:text-base","children":"Participants are expected to maintain a smart casual or formal dress code throughout the event."}]]}],["$","details","7️⃣ What do I need to bring for the event?",{"className":"group rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/25 bg-black/35 px-5 py-4 text-white/85","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white marker:content-none md:text-base","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"7️⃣ What do I need to bring for the event?"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-purple-300 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180","children":"▼"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm leading